def restore_square_vertices(x1, y1, x2, y2):
    x3 = y3 = x4 = y4 = 0
    if x1 == x2 and y1 == y2:
        return -1, -1, -1, -1

    x3 = x1 + (x2 - x1)
    y3 = y1 + (y2 - y1)
    x4 = x1 - (y2 - y1)
    y4 = y1 + (x2 - x1)
    return x3, y3, x4, y4
